node.text:
2019 was an incredible year for Cisco Brewers & we feel like we are on vacation EVERYDAY working, living and breathing Cisco Brewers... because we love our occupations. 🤙🥇💯
.
.
January 1, 2020 marks our 25th year as a brewery & we are so thankful to #CiscoNation for all the love & support. Here’s to another 25! 🍻❤️
.
Video credit to our boy @tweeddreams. You da man!

node.text:
Guess whose back 👀 🍻 We’re so stoked to have @nantucketyler back behind the wood for his 12th season!!

After a long recovery from heart surgery and a ruptured achilles we finally have our good vibes king with us again ~ we love you Tyler Herrick ~ let’s do this 👊🏼🤝.

#family #ciscobrewers #nicebeerifyoucangetit #nantucket #ack #summer #2021

node.text:
The perfect remedy for a 97-degree heat wave: an ice cold cooler of Cisco Hard Teas. …Which flavor are you pulling first: 🍋 🍑 🫐 🍊???

These 130 calorie teas have been flying at our brewpubs this month, and should be available throughout New England at your local package store! Ask if you don’t see ‘em!

They’re 5% ABV and come in 4 different flavors. 

If you haven’t tried them yet… you’re missing out!

#nicebeerifyoucangetit #niceteaifyoucangetit 

@ciscobrewersportsmouth @ciscobrewersseaport @ciscobrewersthevillage @ciscobrewersnewbedford #hardicetea #nantucket #capecodlife #capecod #southshorema #boston #portsmouthnh #drinklocalma #stamfordct #newbedfordma 

📷: @tuckerbeatty
